column9: The '010'. Working class pride. Modern architecture and Europe's largest port.
The '020'. Canal Ring (UNESCO). Liberal culture and global tourism hub.
Central railway hub. Medieval center with unique wharf cellars.
The 'Brainport'. Philips heritage. High-tech and design capital.
Oldest city claim. Birthplace of the EU (Maastricht Treaty). Burgundian lifestyle.
Historic student city of the North. 'Martinitoren' landmark.
Seat of Government & Royal Family. International Court of Justice ('Peace Palace').
